'''Khalil Duhoki''' or '''Xelîl Duhokî''' (born 1951) is a [[Kurdish people|Kurdish]] writer, poet. He was born in [[Duhok, Iraq|Duhok]] in [[Iraqi Kurdistan]]. He began writing poems in 1970. He has been active in several [[Kurdish language|Kurdish]] journals, such as ''Berbang'' published in [[Sweden]]. He is a member of the ''Swedish Writers Union'' [https://web.archive.org/web/20021207182137/http://www.forfattarforbundet.se/in_english/information_eng.html]. 

